### shadcn/ui components

`Badge`, `Button`, `Dialog`, `ScrollArea`, `Separator`, `Tooltip` — all customized to use the CSS custom properties from `theme.css` instead of shadcn's default palette.

`Button` and `Badge` use `class-variance-authority` (CVA) for variant composition.

### Tailwind

Tailwind 3 configured with `content` paths covering all TSX/TS source files. Custom tokens in `tailwind.config.js` map to the CSS custom property names so both Tailwind utilities and raw `var()` references work interchangeably.

